> +			FE_CAN_TRANSMISSION_MODE_AUTO | FE_CAN_GUARD_INTERVAL_AUTO | FE_CAN_HIERARCHY_AUTO,
> +	},
> +	.read_snr = pt3s_read_snr,

Please use, instead, the DVBv5 way to get statistics.

